00:19:32,420 --> 00:19:35,460
In his biography of H.P. Lovecraft, fittingly entitled

282
00:19:35,460 --> 00:19:38,020
Against the World Against Life,

283
00:19:38,020 --> 00:19:39,780
Michel Houellebecq writes,

284
00:19:39,780 --> 00:19:42,100
The character of Lovecraft fascinates us,

285
00:19:42,100 --> 00:19:45,860
partly because his system of values is entirely opposed to ours.

286
00:19:45,860 --> 00:19:48,340
Fundamentally racist, openly reactionary,

287
00:19:48,340 --> 00:19:52,180
he glorifies Puritan inhibition and quite evidently finds repellent

288
00:19:52,180 --> 00:19:54,420
any open display of eroticism.

289
00:19:54,420 --> 00:19:56,980
Resolutely anti-commercial, he despises money,

290
00:19:56,980 --> 00:20:00,500
considers democracy to be pure folly, progress an illusion.

291
00:20:00,500 --> 00:20:05,140
The word liberty, so dear to Americans, elicits from him only a gloomy sneer.

292
00:20:05,140 --> 00:20:08,740
All his life he maintained a typically aristocratic attitude of scorn

293
00:20:08,740 --> 00:20:12,180
for humanity in general together with an extreme solicitude

294
00:20:12,180 --> 00:20:14,420
toward individuals in person.

295
00:20:14,420 --> 00:20:17,380
Houellebecq kinda sucks, honestly,

296
00:20:17,380 --> 00:20:20,740
and idolizes some of Lovecraft's worst qualities in his biography,

297
00:20:20,740 --> 00:20:23,140
but this quote is helpful in illustrating the specifics

298
00:20:23,140 --> 00:20:25,300
of Lovecraft's worldview, so I'm gonna use it.

299
00:20:25,300 --> 00:20:28,260
A stopped clock is right twice a day, I suppose.

300
00:20:28,260 --> 00:20:31,140
Lovecraft seemingly hated society itself,

301
00:20:31,140 --> 00:20:33,540
but he had a deeper and specific dislike

302
00:20:33,540 --> 00:20:36,180
for Black and Jewish people along with immigrants.

303
00:20:36,180 --> 00:20:40,340
It's so prevalent in his writing that even citing multiple examples

304
00:20:40,340 --> 00:20:43,460
would kind of diminish how overwhelming and constant it is.

305
00:20:43,460 --> 00:20:48,020
I can't even bring myself to say the name of Lovecraft's cat

306
00:20:48,020 --> 00:20:49,860
because it's a racial slur.

307
00:20:49,860 --> 00:20:54,100
And despite this obviously completely full schedule of racism

308
00:20:54,100 --> 00:20:56,820
and general hatred for humanity itself,

309
00:20:56,820 --> 00:20:59,940
he also managed to find time to be a raging homophobe.

310
00:20:59,940 --> 00:21:02,660
He claimed not to have even known homosexuality existed

311
00:21:02,660 --> 00:21:04,340
until he was in his 30s,

312
00:21:04,340 --> 00:21:07,860
