313
00:21:07,860 --> 00:21:10,900
You know, growing up, I always would immediately try to find ways

314
00:21:10,900 --> 00:21:13,860
to write off or handwave away the racism.

315
00:21:13,860 --> 00:21:17,060
You know, I would say, well, it was a part of his time.

316
00:21:17,060 --> 00:21:19,940
