317
00:21:19,940 --> 00:21:22,900
to just say, God, what a piece of shit.

318
00:21:24,100 --> 00:21:27,620
I mean, honestly, like, his work meant something to me

319
00:21:27,620 --> 00:21:29,780
in a really, like, profound way

320
00:21:29,780 --> 00:21:31,460
that no other work has ever really done,

321
00:21:32,340 --> 00:21:34,900
but I fucking think the guy's terrible.

322
00:21:34,900 --> 00:21:38,500
