325
00:21:42,340 --> 00:21:44,340
and defiant ignorance of reactionaries

326
00:21:44,340 --> 00:21:45,940
because he used to be one.

327
00:21:45,940 --> 00:21:49,140
"'I know how smugly ignorant I was,' he wrote.

328
00:21:49,140 --> 00:21:51,780
