329
00:21:51,780 --> 00:21:53,060
and supported the New Deal,

330
00:21:53,060 --> 00:21:55,300
and he was married to a Jewish woman for a while,

331
00:21:55,300 --> 00:21:58,900
but it's debatable whether he really developed all that much,

332
00:21:58,980 --> 00:22:02,500
and the racism in his work is still unavoidably there.'"

