369
00:23:41,860 --> 00:23:44,500
not some generic fear of outsiders,

370
00:23:45,220 --> 00:23:49,860
but the anxieties and fears that come with being an outsider,

371
00:23:50,420 --> 00:23:53,860
of being in a world that doesn't really understand you,

372
00:23:53,860 --> 00:23:58,180
and perhaps of not being fully able to understand yourself.

373
00:23:58,180 --> 00:24:00,340
So there is a fairly decent reason here

374
00:24:00,340 --> 00:24:02,340
why someone might be drawn to these works,

375
00:24:02,340 --> 00:24:04,820
even if the author was deeply problematic.

376
00:24:04,820 --> 00:24:07,300
