383
00:24:19,620 --> 00:24:21,940
who he worked closely with on numerous stories

384
00:24:21,940 --> 00:24:24,740
and who Lovecraft made the executor of his literary estate

385
00:24:24,740 --> 00:24:25,860
in the event of his death.

386
00:24:25,860 --> 00:24:27,380
It's partially due to Barlow

387
00:24:27,380 --> 00:24:28,900
that so much of Lovecraft's writing

388
00:24:28,900 --> 00:24:30,260
